{"tid":2054970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國反警暴「黑色經濟圈」概念急速興起   以真金白銀消費支持同路人","createTime":"2020-06-07T14:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T17:31:47.000Z","uid":358086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0381ebaeaa5f57e6405669e8b6daf20ed76f234e","tid":2054970,"uid":358086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50zkVv5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50zkVv5.png&h=47391290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信在過去一年都對香港的「黃色經濟圈」並不陌生。最近美國發生致命的警暴事件，引發一連串反對種族歧視的示威抗議活動，相關的文宣、檔案和程式開始在網絡廣泛流傳，而類似香港的「黑色經濟圈」概念亦成為大熱。<br />\n<br />\n「黑色經濟圈」不但在手機程式下載量中反映出來，抗議種族歧視的網民亦開始使用 #blackownedbusiness 的 hashtag 去標示由黑人經營的商店以表示支持。網上亦開始流傳由食評家 Soleil Ho 提供的「黑色食肆」清單，該試算表甚至因為太多人閱覽，令載入的速度變慢。就連大企業亦有份推動「黑色經濟圈」，外賣送貨的 Uber Eats 重點推介少數族裔經營的食肆，又在年底前免收黑人經營食肆的送貨費用作為支持。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/06/07/black-owned-business-app-downloads/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F06%2F07%2Fblack-owned-business-app-downloads%2Flife-tech%2F&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=b3cdd38f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/06/07/black-owned-business-app-downloads/life-tech/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">附送五毛生氣圖</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G2yt4s8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG2yt4s8.png&h=6274b61d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6cwWtTm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6cwWtTm.png&h=52ab257a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c513dfdba5bf2853bcae7f579ef509e19f7508f2","tid":2054970,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0381ebaeaa5f57e6405669e8b6daf20ed76f234e","tid":2054970,"uid":358086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl